			"value": "<p><em>You call out to a creature and salute them, telling them to be brave and magically lessening the weight of their fears.</em></p><p><strong>Buff</strong></p><ul><li><p>The creature is immune to being &amp;reference[Frightened] and gains Temporary Hit Points equal to your spellcasting ability modifier at the start of each of its turns. When the spell ends, the target loses any remaining temporary hit points from this spell.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Upcasting:</strong> Target one additional creature for each spell level above 1st.</p>",
